data.description: This Colonial style embankment style home offers an open floor plan. The first floor consists of a living room/dining room area leading out to a deck overlooking a private backyard. Fully applianced kitchen features granite countertops and a breakfast bar. Oversized master bedroom with walk in closet and master bathroom. Two additional bedrooms, family bath and laundry complete the upper level. See Agent to Agent Remarks.
